      "span_text": "The low face validity of PK items with respect to PTSD adds to its clinical utility in assessing PTSD. A second focus of this study was to evaluate the relationship between characteristics of the victim and the trauma, and PTSD. Contrary to previous research with battered women and crime victims (Dutton et al., 1990;  ), significant differences for race were observed between the PTSD groups."
